Sampai aku kembali,

74
00:06:05,115 --> 00:06:08,702
jika aku berpura-pura bodoh dan serakah,

75
00:06:09,911 --> 00:06:11,162
apakah itu salah?

76
00:06:17,168 --> 00:06:19,169
DI MUSIM BERCAHAYA ANDA

77
00:06:20,922 --> 00:06:22,507
