725
00:44:23,619 --> 00:44:25,538
Dia mulai tersenyum lagi baru-baru ini.

726
00:44:26,622 --> 00:44:29,499
Saya tahu saya bertemu orang hebat.

727
00:44:29,500 --> 00:44:31,252
Saya merasa bersyukur.

728
00:44:32,253 --> 00:44:33,880
